navigations-desc.span1: Participate on our contests and show

socialTitle: GO SOCIAL AND SEE WHAT THEY SAY ABOUT US!

howitWork.title: HOW IT WORKS
howitWork.list1: Choose one of the listed contests
howitWork.list2: Pay the value to submit your photos
howitWork.list3: Upload your photos or send it by email (in case of bank transfer)
howitWork.list4: Wait until the end of the contest (end or REVIEW phase)
howitWork.list5: The results will be sent to your email address with the final list of winners and your photo final position. You will also be informed about the judge decision based on this criteria
